top", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "JuZiSang", "btc": "", "location": "深圳", "tagline": "唔~", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a07/aa35/207485_mini.png?m=1689644959", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a07/aa35/207485_normal.png?m=1689644959", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a07/aa35/207485_large.png?m=1689644959", "created": 1482596813, "last_modified": 1689644959}, "last_reply_by": "hancai", "last_touched": 1697482110, "title": "关于程序员秃头，从梗到刻板印象", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/982338", "created": 1697424990, "deleted": 0, "content": "现实中，第一次知道你干什么的亲戚朋友会问，做这个是不是很掉头发。\r\n还有人老是会用这个调侃，最令人讨厌的是有人经常性用嘲讽的语气反复发问。\r\n甚至有点蔓延的趋势，上周去种了颗呀，就有人问：你们程序员还掉牙？\r\n\r\n基本已经成刻板印象了吧。\r\n\r\n怎么不失礼貌的回答，或者有冲击力的回怼？\r\n\r\n或者分享下你们会被经常问是不是秃头吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>现实中，第一次知道你干什么的亲戚朋友会问，做这个是不是很掉头发。\n还有人老是会用这个调侃，最令人讨厌的是有人经常性用嘲讽的语气反复发问。\n甚至有点蔓延的趋势，上周去种了颗呀，就有人问：你们程序员还掉牙？</p>\n<p>基本已经成刻板印象了吧。</p>\n<p>怎么不失礼貌的回答，或者有冲击力的回怼？</p>\n<p>或者分享下你们会被经常问是不是秃头吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1697424990, "replies": 82, "id": 982338}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 59486, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8674, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 654502, "username": "temporarily", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/temporarily", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8ebee38e4e611850d8df5ad87dd43363?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8ebee38